videos.headline: Lamar Jackson bursts through Boston College defense for TD
videos.description: Lamar Jackson keeps it himself and gets through the Boston College defense for a 69-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson uses his arm to get another Louisville TD
videos.description: Lamar Jackson throws to James Quick for the 30-yard touchdown give Louisville a 14-0 lead over Boston College.

videos.headline: Jackson throws deep again for third TD of 1st quarter
videos.description: After already running in a touchdown and throwing for another score, Lamar Jackson throws deep and connects with Jeremy Smith for a 44-yard touchdown to extend Louisville's lead over Boston College to 21-0.

videos.headline: Boston College fumbles in own territory
videos.description: Boston College fumbles in own territory

videos.headline: Jackson throws to Quick again for another TD
videos.description: Lamar Jackson drops back and finds James Quick, who scampers into the end zone for a 10-yard touchdown to give Louisville a 28-0 lead over Boston College.

videos.headline: Jackson throws fourth TD pass of first half
videos.description: Lamar Jackson gets his fourth touchdown pass of the game with a five-yard strike to Cole Hikutini, giving Louisville a 35-0 lead over Boston College.

videos.headline: P. Towles pass intercepted by C. Williams
videos.description: Patrick Towles pass intercepted Chucky Williams return for 20 yds to the BC 40

videos.headline: L. Jackson pass intercepted by J. Johnson
videos.description: Lamar Jackson pass intercepted John Johnson return for 22 yds to the BC 30

videos.headline: Boston College fumbles again
videos.description: Patrick Towles sacked by James Hearns for a loss of 12 yards to the BC 28 Patrick Towles fumbled, forced by James Hearns, recovered by Lvile DeAngelo Brown , return for 0 yards

videos.headline: Jackson turns it over for second time
videos.description: Lamar Jackson run for 1 yd to the Lvile 42 Lamar Jackson fumbled, forced by Kevin Kavalec, recovered by BC Connor Strachan

videos.headline: Boston College finally gets on the board
videos.description: Patrick Towles throws a short pass to Tyler Rouse, who manages to get by the Louisville defense for the 39-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jackson runs it in for sixth total TD of game
videos.description: Lamar Jackson keeps it himself for the 13-yard touchdown run to put Louisville up 45-7 over Boston College.

videos.headline: Jackson cuts through BC defense for third rushing TD of game
videos.description: Lamar Jackson gets his third rushing touchdown of the game by forcing his way through the Boston College defense for a 53-yard score.  It's the seventh total touchdown of the game for Jackson.

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson destroys BC with seven touchdowns
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson shows no regard for Boston College's defense, recording four passing touchdowns and three rushing scores. He finishes the game with 231 yards passing and 185 yards rushing in the Cardinals' blowout win over the Eagles.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Lamar Jackson destroys BC with seven touchdowns) 2016/11/05 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Jackson accounts for seven TDs as Louisville rolls to win
videos.description: Lamar Jackson throws for four touchdowns and rushes for three more scores as No. 7 Louisville defeats Boston College 52-7.
